{"tid":1651070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想去狗屋附近玩屎，有無人一齊？","createTime":"2019-10-13T08:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T12:14:28.000Z","uid":304769,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2d20a66a2a91ae5d537e001a41ac037f3b8da2","tid":1651070,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:33:07.000Z","msg":"屎彈很好玩，但好似現在很少人玩。<br />\n方法：<br />\n1.預備膠袋，密實袋，金魚袋，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記得先入水做防漏測試！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n2.屙屎入去，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">捻碎，越爛越好，加入暖水</span></strong>（尿效果更好）<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不要讓膠袋的tension太大</span></strong>，也不要有空氣<br />\n小心打死結綁緊，再用象筋封好<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.合法攜帶，不是攻擊性武器<br />\n2.視覺觸覺嗅覺味覺效果極佳<br />\n效果示意圖<br />\n壞處：<br />\n小心自己都變周紳士"},{"pid":"9397f8077ef811ecfd39e155952631a9cc92df12","tid":1651070,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51c2695ac1596c0bc5a394fa6d04c0d2f9735133","tid":1651070,"uid":139677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08632bf9846e75ff258ee690e0b5e70ed8f6f9fb","tid":1651070,"uid":298385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc9a20b67eb44b761d13502c7e2e6656ddec851","tid":1651070,"uid":116143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:37:03.000Z","msg":"ok喎! 食屎狗!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfa994003f01bdfd228d45a65ef7f35837c2377","tid":1651070,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9397f8077ef811ecfd39e155952631a9cc92df12","tid":1651070,"uid":181778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T08:36:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,